  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Board has chosen you for its newest experiment.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148490/extras/8aaf4392fa197aa549eb9e9814bc4c5b.avif?t=1748314124\" width=600 height=600 /></span>Play as an up-and-coming Agent given the impossible task of delving into the mind of an unreadable beast. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148490/extras/7f74fbfcc84ce795b4d75b205af17aa3.avif?t=1748314124\" width=600 height=600 /></span>The chamber walls are cold and uninviting, one sole light illuminating the <i> thing </i> waiting inside.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your heart beats loudly in the silence, an uncontrollable sign of your rising paranoia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The unnerving presence of the monster fills you with honest,  unshakeable fear. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How the next three days progress is entirely up to you: your methods of interrogation must be finely tuned and given purposeful direction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Being unable to choose a side won't end well, so don't idle on the side lines. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148490/extras/a1afbae631077e437603257b65d4b77c.avif?t=1748314124\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interrogate Subject 6244.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your primary goal is extraction of as much information about this creature as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether or not you're added to 6244's body count isn't always up to you, but your decisions matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148490/extras/98fd660595f2e019fbb1360fdc3c5928.avif?t=1748314124\" width=600 height=600 /></span><strong><u>Don't end up another casualty.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>See you soon, Agent. </i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Board has chosen you for its newest experiment.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148490/extras/8aaf4392fa197aa549eb9e9814bc4c5b.avif?t=1748314124\" width=600 height=600 /></span>Play as an up-and-coming Agent given the impossible task of delving into the mind of an unreadable beast. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148490/extras/7f74fbfcc84ce795b4d75b205af17aa3.avif?t=1748314124\" width=600 height=600 /></span>The chamber walls are cold and uninviting, one sole light illuminating the <i> thing </i> waiting inside.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your heart beats loudly in the silence, an uncontrollable sign of your rising paranoia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The unnerving presence of the monster fills you with honest,  unshakeable fear. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How the next three days progress is entirely up to you: your methods of interrogation must be finely tuned and given purposeful direction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Being unable to choose a side won't end well, so don't idle on the side lines. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148490/extras/a1afbae631077e437603257b65d4b77c.avif?t=1748314124\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interrogate Subject 6244.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your primary goal is extraction of as much information about this creature as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether or not you're added to 6244's body count isn't always up to you, but your decisions matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148490/extras/98fd660595f2e019fbb1360fdc3c5928.avif?t=1748314124\" width=600 height=600 /></span><strong><u>Don't end up another casualty.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>See you soon, Agent. </i></p>",
